title: When you finally reach Diamond V

replies.body:
enjoy it, my man.

you deserve it

I only ARAM, but congrats bro.
I'm not a 'great' player, but friends say to me "that ARAM ELO", when they see me unranked in a team full of plats and diamonds most games.

Nice congrats! When I find my groove I aim to concentrate on ranked only and reach gold. That's my goal.
Diamond is beyond my skill level, atleast for now. But I think achieving anything beyond gold is a fair feat of accomplishment. Enjoy those feels xD
Gj mate time for masters with the Blob carries :^)
